            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped chives</strong> and <strong>soured cream </strong>in a small bowl and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>soured cream & chive dip</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1658234460804-x200.jpg",
