            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and <strong>grated carrot</strong> to a bowl and toss everything together – this is your <strong>carrot salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1658234465239-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
