          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1658234465239-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Discard all the excess marinade from the chicken</p><p>Add your <strong>cracked black pepper</strong>,<strong> ground paprika</strong>, <strong>cornflour </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>to the bowl with the <strong>marinated chicken</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up until the <strong>chicken</strong> is fully coated</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1658234468961-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1658234468961-x400.jpg",
