            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy chicken strips</strong> with the<strong> chips</strong> and <strong>carrot salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Dollop the <strong>soured cream & chive </strong>and <strong>sweet chilli dips </strong>to the side, get dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
